(151, 2, 86, '2-12-3-2', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Cybersecurity Event Logs and Monitoring Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for event logs and monitoring management must include Activation of cybersecurity event logs on remote access and privileged user accounts.', '2022-02-25 01:04:13', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(152, 2, 86, '2-12-3-3', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Cybersecurity Event Logs and Monitoring Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for event logs and monitoring management must include Identification of required technologies (e.g., SIEM) for cybersecurity event logs collection.', '2022-02-25 01:04:46', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(153, 2, 86, '2-12-3-4', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Cybersecurity Event Logs and Monitoring Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for event logs and monitoring management must include Continuous monitoring of cybersecurity events.', '2022-02-25 01:05:13', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(154, 2, 86, '2-12-3-5', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Cybersecurity Event Logs and Monitoring Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for event logs and monitoring management must include Retention period for cybersecurity event logs (must be 12 months minimum).', '2022-02-25 01:05:37', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(155, 2, 83, '2-11-3-1', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Penetration Testing > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for penetration testing processes must include Scope of penetration tests which must cover Internet-facing services and its technical components including infrastructure, websites, web applications, mobile apps, email and remote access.', '2022-02-25 01:07:30', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(156, 2, 83, '2-11-3-2', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Penetration Testing > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for penetration testing processes must include Conducting penetration tests periodically.', '2022-02-25 01:07:50', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(157, 2, 79, '2-10-3-1', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Vulnerabilities Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for technical vulnerabilities management must include  Periodic vulnerabilities assessments.', '2022-02-25 01:09:31', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(158, 2, 79, '2-10-3-2', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Vulnerabilities Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for technical vulnerabilities management must include  Vulnerabilities classification based on criticality level.', '2022-02-25 01:10:43', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(159, 2, 79, '2-10-3-3', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Vulnerabilities Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for technical vulnerabilities management must include  Vulnerabilities remediation based on classification and associated risk levels.', '2022-02-25 01:11:11', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(160, 2, 79, '2-10-3-4', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Vulnerabilities Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for technical vulnerabilities management must include  Security patch management.', '2022-02-25 01:11:43', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(161, 2, 79, '2-10-3-5', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Vulnerabilities Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for technical vulnerabilities management must include  Subscription with authorized and trusted cybersecurity resources for up-to-date information and notifications on technical vulnerabilities.', '2022-02-25 01:12:11', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(162, 2, 75, '2-9-3-1', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Backup and Recovery Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for backup and recovery management must include Scope and coverage of backups to cover critical technology and information assets.', '2022-02-25 01:13:29', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(163, 2, 75, '2-9-3-2', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Backup and Recovery Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for backup and recovery management must include Ability to perform quick recovery of data and systems after cybersecurity incidents.', '2022-02-25 01:13:51', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(164, 2, 75, '2-9-3-3', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Backup and Recovery Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for backup and recovery management must include Periodic tests of backups recovery effectiveness.', '2022-02-25 01:15:57', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(165, 2, 71, '2-8-3-1', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Cryptography > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for cryptography must include Approved cryptographic solutions standards and its technical and regulatory limitations.', '2022-02-25 01:17:53', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(166, 2, 71, '2-8-3-2', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Cryptography > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for cryptography must include Secure management of cryptographic keys during their lifecycles.', '2022-02-25 01:18:15', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(167, 2, 71, '2-8-3-3', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Cryptography > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for cryptography must include Encryption of data in-transit and at-rest as per classification and related laws and regulations.', '2022-02-25 01:18:39', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(168, 2, 67, '2-7-3-1', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Data and Information Protection > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for protecting and handling data and information must include Data and information ownership.', '2022-02-25 01:20:10', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(169, 2, 67, '2-7-3-2', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Data and Information Protection > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for protecting and handling data and information must include Data and information classification and labeling mechanisms.', '2022-02-25 01:20:32', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(170, 2, 67, '2-7-3-3', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Data and Information Protection > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for protecting and handling data and information must include Data and information privacy.', '2022-02-25 01:20:52', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(171, 2, 63, '2-6-3-1', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Mobile Devices Security > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for mobile devices security and BYOD must include Separation and encryption of organizations data and information stored on mobile devices and BYODs.', '2022-02-25 01:22:35', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(172, 2, 63, '2-6-3-2', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Mobile Devices Security > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for mobile devices security and BYOD must include Controlled and restricted use based on job requirements.', '2022-02-25 01:23:01', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(173, 2, 63, '2-6-3-3', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Mobile Devices Security > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for mobile devices security and BYOD must include Secure wiping of organizations data and information stored on mobile devices and BYOD in cases of device loss, theft or after termination/separation from the organization.', '2022-02-25 01:23:23', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(174, 2, 63, '2-6-3-4', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Mobile Devices Security > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for mobile devices security and BYOD must include Security awareness for mobile devices users.', '2022-02-25 01:23:44', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(175, 2, 59, '2-5-3-1', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Networks Security Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for network security management must include Logical or physical segregation and segmentation of network segments using firewalls and defense-in-depth principles.', '2022-02-25 01:25:29', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(176, 2, 59, '2-5-3-2', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Networks Security Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for network security management must include Network segregation between production, test and development environments.', '2022-02-25 01:25:48', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(177, 2, 59, '2-5-3-3', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Networks Security Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for network security management must include Secure browsing and Internet connectivity including restrictions on the use of file storage/sharing and remote access websites, and protection against suspicious websites.', '2022-02-25 01:26:10', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(178, 2, 59, '2-5-3-4', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Networks Security Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for network security management must include Wireless network protection using strong authentication and encryption techniques. A comprehensive risk assessment and management exercise must be conducted to assess and manage the cyber risks prior to connecting any wireless networks to the organizations internal network.', '2022-02-25 01:26:30', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(179, 2, 59, '2-5-3-5', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Networks Security Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for network security management must include Management and restrictions on network services, protocols and ports.', '2022-02-25 01:27:02', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(180, 2, 59, '2-5-3-6', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Networks Security Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for network security management must include Intrusion Prevention Systems (IPS).', '2022-02-25 01:27:24', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(181, 2, 59, '2-5-3-7', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Networks Security Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for network security management must include Security of Domain Name Service (DNS).', '2022-02-25 01:27:49', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(182, 2, 59, '2-5-3-8', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Networks Security Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for network security management must include Secure management and protection of Internet browsing channel against Advanced Persistent Threats (APT), which normally utilize zero-day viruses and malware.', '2022-02-25 01:28:38', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(183, 2, 55, '2-4-3-1', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Email Protection > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for protecting the email service must include Analyzing and filtering email messages (specifically phishing emails and spam) using advanced and up-to-date email protection techniques.', '2022-02-25 01:30:15', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(184, 2, 55, '2-4-3-2', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Email Protection > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for protecting the email service must include Multi-factor authentication for remote and webmail access to email service.', '2022-02-25 01:30:41', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(185, 2, 55, '2-4-3-3', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Email Protection > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for protecting the email service must include Email archiving and backup.', '2022-02-25 01:31:05', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(186, 2, 55, '2-4-3-4', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Email Protection > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for protecting the email service must include Secure management and protection against Advanced Persistent Threats (APT), which normally utilize zero-day viruses and malware.', '2022-02-25 01:31:27', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(187, 2, 55, '2-4-3-5', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Email Protection > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for protecting the email service must include Validation of the organizations email service domains (e.g., using Sender Policy Framework (SPF)).', '2022-02-25 01:31:44', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(188, 2, 47, '2-2-3-1', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Identity and Access Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for identity and access management must include User authentication based on username and password.', '2022-02-25 01:33:54', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(189, 2, 47, '2-2-3-2', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Identity and Access Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for identity and access management must include Multi-factor authentication for remote access.', '2022-02-25 01:34:18', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(190, 2, 47, '2-2-3-3', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Identity and Access Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for identity and access management must include User authorization based on identity and access control principles: Need-to-Know and Need-to-Use, Least Privilege and Segregation of Duties.', '2022-02-25 01:34:41', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(191, 2, 47, '2-2-3-4', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Identity and Access Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for identity and access management must include Privileged access management.', '2022-02-25 01:35:05', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(192, 2, 47, '2-2-3-5', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Identity and Access Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for identity and access management must include Periodic review of users identities and access rights.', '2022-02-25 01:35:26', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(193, 2, 51, '2-3-3-1', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Information System and Information Processing Facilities Protection > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for protecting information systems and information processing facilities must include Advanced, up-to-date and secure management of malware and virus protection on servers and workstations.', '2022-02-25 01:36:54', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(194, 2, 51, '2-3-3-2', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Information System and Information Processing Facilities Protection > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for protecting information systems and information processing facilities must include Restricted use and secure handling of external storage media.', '2022-02-25 01:37:17', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(195, 2, 51, '2-3-3-3', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Information System and Information Processing Facilities Protection > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for protecting information systems and information processing facilities must include Patch management for information systems, software and devices.', '2022-02-25 01:37:44', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(196, 2, 51, '2-3-3-4', 'Cybersecurity Defense > Information System and Information Processing Facilities Protection > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements for protecting information systems and information processing facilities must include Centralized clock synchronization with an accurate and trusted source (e.g., Saudi Standards, Metrology and Quality Organization (SASO)).', '2022-02-25 01:38:09', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(197, 2, 36, '1-10-3-1', 'Cybersecurity Governance > Cybersecurity Awareness and Training Program > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity awareness program must cover the latest cyber threats and how to protect against them, and must include Secure handling of email services, especially phishing emails.', '2022-02-25 01:41:05', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(198, 2, 36, '1-10-3-2', 'Cybersecurity Governance > Cybersecurity Awareness and Training Program > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity awareness program must cover the latest cyber threats and how to protect against them, and must include Secure handling of mobile devices and storage media.', '2022-02-25 01:41:29', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(199, 2, 36, '1-10-3-3', 'Cybersecurity Governance > Cybersecurity Awareness and Training Program > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity awareness program must cover the latest cyber threats and how to protect against them, and must include Secure Internet browsing.', '2022-02-25 01:41:49', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(200, 2, 36, '1-10-3-4', 'Cybersecurity Governance > Cybersecurity Awareness and Training Program > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity awareness program must cover the latest cyber threats and how to protect against them, and must include Secure use of social media.', '2022-02-25 01:42:12', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(201, 2, 31, '1-9-4-1', 'Cybersecurity Governance > Cybersecurity in Human Resources > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The personnel cybersecurity requirements during employment must include Cybersecurity awareness (during on-boarding and during employment).', '2022-02-25 01:43:26', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(202, 2, 31, '1-9-4-2', 'Cybersecurity Governance > Cybersecurity in Human Resources > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The personnel cybersecurity requirements during employment must include Implementation of and compliance with the cybersecurity requirements as per the organizational cybersecurity policies and procedures.', '2022-02-25 01:43:48', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(203, 2, 30, '1-9-3-1', 'Cybersecurity Governance > Cybersecurity in Human Resources > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The personnel cybersecurity requirements prior to employment must include Inclusion of personnel cybersecurity responsibilities and non-disclosure clauses (covering the cybersecurity requirements during employment and after termination/separation) in employment contracts.', '2022-02-25 01:45:11', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(204, 2, 30, '1-9-3-2', 'Cybersecurity Governance > Cybersecurity in Human Resources > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The personnel cybersecurity requirements prior to employment must include Screening or vetting candidates of cybersecurity and critical/privileged positions.', '2022-02-25 01:45:30', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(205, 2, 21, '1-6-3-1', 'Cybersecurity Governance > Cybersecurity in Information and Technology Project Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements related to software and application development projects must include Using secure coding standards.', '2022-02-25 01:47:03', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(206, 2, 21, '1-6-3-2', 'Cybersecurity Governance > Cybersecurity in Information and Technology Project Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements related to software and application development projects must include Using trusted and licensed sources for software development tools and libraries.', '2022-02-25 01:47:29', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(207, 2, 21, '1-6-3-3', 'Cybersecurity Governance > Cybersecurity in Information and Technology Project Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements related to software and application development projects must include Conducting compliance test for software against the defined organizational cybersecurity requirements.', '2022-02-25 01:47:51', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(208, 2, 21, '1-6-3-4', 'Cybersecurity Governance > Cybersecurity in Information and Technology Project Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements related to software and application development projects must include Secure integration between software components.', '2022-02-25 01:48:13', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(209, 2, 21, '1-6-3-5', 'Cybersecurity Governance > Cybersecurity in Information and Technology Project Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements related to software and application development projects must include Conducting a configurations review, secure configuration and hardening and patching before going live for software products.', '2022-02-25 01:48:33', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(210, 2, 20, '1-6-2-1', 'Cybersecurity Governance > Cybersecurity in Information and Technology Project Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements in project and assets (information/technology) change management must include Vulnerability assessment and remediation.', '2022-02-25 01:49:55', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(211, 2, 20, '1-6-2-2', 'Cybersecurity Governance > Cybersecurity in Information and Technology Project Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity requirements in project and assets (information/technology) change management must include Conducting a configurations review, secure configuration and hardening and patching before changes or going live for technology projects.', '2022-02-25 01:50:20', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(212, 2, 17, '1-5-3-1', 'Cybersecurity Governance > Cybersecurity Risk Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity risk assessment procedures must be implemented at Early stages of technology projects.', '2022-02-25 01:52:38', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(213, 2, 17, '1-5-3-2', 'Cybersecurity Governance > Cybersecurity Risk Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity risk assessment procedures must be implemented Before making major changes to technology infrastructure.', '2022-02-25 01:52:57', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(214, 2, 17, '1-5-3-3', 'Cybersecurity Governance > Cybersecurity Risk Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity risk assessment procedures must be implemented During the planning phase of obtaining third party services.', '2022-02-25 01:53:16', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(215, 2, 17, '1-5-3-4', 'Cybersecurity Governance > Cybersecurity Risk Management > Controls > Sub-Controls', 'The cybersecurity risk assessment procedures must be implemented During the planning phase and before going live for new technology services and products.', '2022-02-25 01:53:36', '2022-03-02 21:53:38'),
(216, 4, NULL, '4.2.2.1', 'Risk Analysis > Business Rational > Control', 'The organization should develop a high-level business rationale as a basis for its effort to manage IACS cyber security, which addresses the unique dependence of the organization on IACS.', '2022-02-25 02:57:47', '2022-02-25 02:57:47'),
(217, 4, NULL, '4.2.3.1', 'Risk Analysis > Risk identification, classification, and assessment >  Control', 'The organization shall select a particular risk assessment and analysis approach and methodology that identifies and prioritizes risks based upon security threats, vulnerabilities and consequences related to its IACS assets.', '2022-02-25 03:02:44', '2022-02-25 03:02:44'),
(218, 4, NULL, '4.2.3.2', 'Risk Analysis > Risk identification, classification, and assessment >  Control', 'The organization should provide participants in the risk assessment activity with appropriate information including methodology training, before beginning to identify the risks.', '2022-02-25 03:03:02', '2022-02-25 03:03:02'),
(219, 4, NULL, '4.2.3.3', 'Risk Analysis > Risk identification, classification, and assessment >  Control', 'A high-level system risk assessment shall be performed to understand the financial and HSE consequences in the event that availability, integrity or confidentiality of the IACS is compromised.', '2022-02-25 03:03:23', '2022-02-25 03:03:23'),
(220, 4, NULL, '4.2.3.4', 'Risk Analysis > Risk identification, classification, and assessment >  Control', 'The organization shall identify the various IACS, gather data about the devices to characterize the nature of the security risk, and group the devices into logical systems.', '2022-02-25 03:03:41', '2022-02-25 03:03:41'),
(221, 4, NULL, '4.2.3.5', 'Risk Analysis > Risk identification, classification, and assessment >  Control', 'The organization shall develop simple network diagrams for each of the logically integrated systems showing the major devices, network types, and general locations of the equipment.', '2022-02-25 03:04:24', '2022-02-25 03:04:24'),
(222, 4, NULL, '4.2.3.6', 'Risk Analysis > Risk identification, classification, and assessment >  Control', 'The organization shall develop the criteria and assign a priority rating for mitigating the risk of each logical control system.', '2022-02-25 03:04:43', '2022-02-25 03:04:43'),
(223, 4, NULL, '4.2.3.7', 'Risk Analysis > Risk identification, classification, and assessment >  Control', 'The organization shall perform a detailed vulnerability assessment of its individual logical IACS, which may be scoped based on the high-level risk assessment results and prioritization of IACS subject to these risks.', '2022-02-25 03:05:02', '2022-02-25 03:05:02'),
(224, 4, NULL, '4.2.3.8', 'Risk Analysis > Risk identification, classification, and assessment >  Control', 'The organizations risk assessment methodology shall include methods for prioritizing detailed vulnerabilities identified in the detailed vulnerability assessment.', '2022-02-25 03:05:18', '2022-02-25 03:05:18'),
(225, 4, NULL, '4.2.3.9', 'Risk Analysis > Risk identification, classification, and assessment >  Control', 'The organization shall conduct a detailed risk assessment incorporating the vulnerabilities identified in the detailed vulnerability assessment .', '2022-02-25 03:05:35', '2022-02-25 03:05:35'),
(226, 4, NULL, '4.2.3.10', 'Risk Analysis > Risk identification, classification, and assessment >  Control', 'The organization shall identify the risk and vulnerability reassessment frequency as well as any reassessment triggering criteria based on technology, organization, or industrial operation changes.', '2022-02-25 03:05:52', '2022-02-25 03:05:52'),
(227, 4, NULL, '4.2.3.11', 'Risk Analysis > Risk identification, classification, and assessment >  Control', 'The results of physical, HSE and cyber security risk assessments shall be integrated to understand the assets overall risk.', '2022-02-25 03:06:10', '2022-02-25 03:06:10'),
(228, 4, NULL, '4.2.3.12', 'Risk Analysis > Risk identification, classification, and assessment >  Control', 'Risk assessments shall be conducted through all stages of the technology lifecycle including development, implementation, changes, and retirement.', '2022-02-25 03:06:27', '2022-02-25 03:06:27'),
(229, 4, NULL, '4.2.3.13', 'Risk Analysis > Risk identification, classification, and assessment >  Control', 'The risk assessment methodology and the results of the risk assessment shall be documented.', '2022-02-25 03:06:44', '2022-02-25 03:06:44'),
(230, 4, NULL, '4.2.3.14', 'Risk Analysis > Risk identification, classification, and assessment >  Control', 'Up-to-date vulnerability assessment records should be maintained for all assets comprising the IACS.', '2022-02-25 03:07:20', '2022-02-25 03:07:20'),
(231, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.2.1', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > CSMS scope >  Control', 'The organization shall develop a formal written scope for the cyber security program.', '2022-02-25 03:07:40', '2022-02-25 03:07:40'),
(232, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.2.2', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > CSMS scope >  Control', 'The scope should explain the strategic goals, process, and timing for the CSMS.', '2022-02-25 03:07:58', '2022-02-25 03:07:58'),
(233, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.3.1', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Organizing for security >  Control', 'The organization shall obtain senior management support for a cyber security program.', '2022-02-25 03:08:16', '2022-02-25 03:08:16'),
(234, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.3.2', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Organizing for security >  Control', 'There shall be an organization, structure or network of stakeholders established (or chosen) under management leadership, with the responsibility to provide clear direction and oversight for the cyber aspects of the IACS.', '2022-02-25 03:08:40', '2022-02-25 03:08:40'),
(235, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.3.3', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Organizing for security >  Control', 'Organizational responsibilities shall be clearly defined for cyber security and related physical security activities.', '2022-02-25 03:08:57', '2022-02-25 03:08:57'),
(236, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.3.4', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Organizing for security >  Control', 'The core team of stakeholders should be crossfunctional in nature to bring together the skills necessary to address security in all parts of the IACS.', '2022-02-25 03:09:15', '2022-02-25 03:09:15'),
(237, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.4.1', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Staff training and security awareness >  Control', 'The organization shall design and implement a cyber security training program.', '2022-02-25 03:09:34', '2022-02-25 03:09:34'),
(238, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.4.2', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Staff training and security awareness >  Control', 'All personnel (including employees, contract employees, and third-party contractors) shall be trained initially and periodically thereafter in the correct security procedures and the correct use of information processing facilities.', '2022-02-25 03:09:52', '2022-02-25 03:09:52'),
(239, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.4.3', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Staff training and security awareness >  Control', 'All personnel that perform risk management, IACS engineering, system administration/maintenance and other tasks that impact the CSMS should be trained on the security objectives and industrial operations for these tasks.', '2022-02-25 03:10:09', '2022-02-25 03:10:09'),
(240, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.4.4', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Staff training and security awareness >  Control', 'The training program should be validated on an ongoing basis to ensure that personnel understand the security program and that they are receiving the proper training.', '2022-02-25 03:10:27', '2022-02-25 03:10:27'),
(241, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.4.5', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Staff training and security awareness >  Control', 'The cyber security training program shall be revised, as necessary, to account for new or changing threats and vulnerabilities.', '2022-02-25 03:10:45', '2022-02-25 03:10:45'),
(242, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.4.6', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Staff training and security awareness >  Control', 'Records of employee training and schedules for training updates should be maintained and reviewed on a regular basis.', '2022-02-25 03:11:02', '2022-02-25 03:11:02'),
(243, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.5.1', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Business continuity plan >  Control', 'Prior to creating a business continuity plan, the organization shall specify recovery objectives for the systems involved based on business needs.', '2022-02-25 03:11:20', '2022-02-25 03:11:20'),
(244, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.5.2', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Business continuity plan >  Control', 'The organization should determine the impact to each system due to a significant disruption and the consequences associated with loss of one or more of the systems.', '2022-02-25 03:11:37', '2022-02-25 03:11:37'),
(245, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.5.3', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Business continuity plan >  Control', 'Continuity plans shall be developed and implemented to ensure that business processes can be restored in accordance with recovery objectives.', '2022-02-25 03:11:54', '2022-02-25 03:11:54'),
(246, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.5.4', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Business continuity plan >  Control', 'A business continuity team should be formed including IACS and other process owners. In the event of a significant disruption, this team should determine the priority of critical business and IACS systems to re-establish operations.', '2022-02-25 03:12:13', '2022-02-25 03:12:13'),
(247, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.5.5', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Business continuity plan >  Control', 'The business continuity plan shall define and communicate the specific roles and responsibilities for each part of the plan.', '2022-02-25 03:12:33', '2022-02-25 03:12:33'),
(248, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.5.6', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Business continuity plan >  Control', 'The organization shall create backup and restore procedures (see 4.3.4.3.9) that support the business continuity plan.', '2022-02-25 03:12:50', '2022-02-25 03:12:50'),
(249, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.5.7', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Business continuity plan >  Control', 'The business continuity plan shall be tested on a regular basis and updated as necessary.', '2022-02-25 03:13:09', '2022-02-25 03:13:09'),
(250, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.6.1', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Security policies and procedures >  Control', 'The organization shall develop high-level cyber security policies for the IACS environment which are approved by management.', '2022-02-25 03:13:26', '2022-02-25 03:13:26'),
(251, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.6.2', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Security policies and procedures >  Control', 'The organization shall develop and approve cyber security procedures, based on the cyber security policies, and provide guidance in how to meet the policies.', '2022-02-25 03:13:44', '2022-02-25 03:13:44'),
(252, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.6.3', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Security policies and procedures >  Control', 'Cyber security policies and procedures that deal with IACS risks should be consistent with or extensions of policies created by other risk management systems.', '2022-02-25 03:13:59', '2022-02-25 03:13:59'),
(253, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.6.4', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Security policies and procedures >  Control', 'Cyber security policies and procedures for the IACS environment shall include compliance requirements.', '2022-02-25 03:14:14', '2022-02-25 03:14:14'),
(254, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.6.5', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Security policies and procedures >  Control', 'The organization shall determine and document its risk tolerance as a basis for creation of policy and risk management activities.', '2022-02-25 03:14:30', '2022-02-25 03:14:30'),
(255, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.6.6', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Security policies and procedures >  Control', 'Cyber security policies and procedures for the IACS environment shall be communicated to all appropriate personnel.', '2022-02-25 03:14:46', '2022-02-25 03:14:46'),
(256, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.6.7', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Security policies and procedures >  Control', 'The cyber security policies and procedures shall be reviewed regularly, validated to confirm that they are up-to-date and being followed, and updated as required to ensure that they remain appropriate.', '2022-02-25 03:15:01', '2022-02-25 03:15:01'),
(257, 4, NULL, '4.3.2.6.8', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Security policy, organization, and awareness > Security policies and procedures >  Control', 'Senior leadership shall demonstrate commitment to cyber security by endorsing the cyber security policies.', '2022-02-25 03:15:18', '2022-02-25 03:15:18'),
(258, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.2.1', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Personnel security >  Control', 'There shall be a personnel security policy established, clearly stating the organizations commitment to security and the security responsibilities of personnel. (Personnel include employees, prospective employees, contract employees, and third-party contractors.)', '2022-02-25 03:15:35', '2022-02-25 03:15:35'),
(259, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.2.2', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Personnel security >  Control', 'Unless government regulation prohibits it, all personnel with access to the IACS (both physical and cyber), including new hires and internal transfers to sensitive positions, shall be screened, including validation of their identity and background checks, during the job application process.', '2022-02-25 03:16:00', '2022-02-25 03:16:00'),
(260, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.2.3', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Personnel security >  Control', 'Personnel should also be subject to ongoing scrutiny for changes that might indicate a conflict of interest or concern for performing the job in an appropriate manner.', '2022-02-25 03:16:17', '2022-02-25 03:16:17'),
(261, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.2.4', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Personnel security >  Control', 'The personnel security policy should address security responsibilities from recruitment through the end of employment, especially for sensitive positions.', '2022-02-25 03:16:34', '2022-02-25 03:16:34'),
(262, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.2.5', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Personnel security >  Control', 'Security expectations and responsibilities shall be clearly documented and regularly communicated to personnel.', '2022-02-25 03:16:52', '2022-02-25 03:16:52'),
(263, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.2.6', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Personnel security >  Control', 'Terms and conditions of employment shall clearly state an employees responsibility for cyber security. These responsibilities shall extend for a reasonable period of time after employment ceases.', '2022-02-25 03:17:08', '2022-02-25 03:17:08'),
(264, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.2.7', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Personnel security >  Control', 'Duties should be segregated among personnel to maintain appropriate checks and balances, so that no single individual has total control over actions that change the functional operation of the IACS.', '2022-02-25 03:17:25', '2022-02-25 03:17:25'),
(265, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.3.1', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Physical and environmental security >  Control', 'Security policies and procedures shall be established that address both physical and cyber security in the protection of assets.', '2022-02-25 03:17:41', '2022-02-25 03:17:41'),
(266, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.3.2', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Physical and environmental security >  Control', 'One or more physical security perimeters shall be established to provide barriers to unauthorized access to protected assets.', '2022-02-25 03:17:57', '2022-02-25 03:17:57'),
(267, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.3.3', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Physical and environmental security >  Control', 'Appropriate entry controls shall be provided at each barrier or boundary.', '2022-02-25 03:18:13', '2022-02-25 03:18:13'),
(268, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.3.4', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Physical and environmental security >  Control', 'Assets shall be protected against environmental damage from threats such as fire, water, smoke, dust, radiation, corrosion, and impact.', '2022-02-25 03:18:29', '2022-02-25 03:18:29'),
(269, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.3.5', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Physical and environmental security >  Control', 'Employees shall be required to follow and enforce the physical security procedures that have been established.', '2022-02-25 03:18:47', '2022-02-25 03:18:47'),
(270, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.3.6', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Physical and environmental security >  Control', 'All connections under the control of the organization shall be adequately protected from tampering or damage.', '2022-02-25 03:19:04', '2022-02-25 03:19:04'),
(271, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.3.7', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Physical and environmental security >  Control', 'All equipment assets, including auxiliary environmental equipment, shall be properly maintained to ensure proper operation.', '2022-02-25 03:19:23', '2022-02-25 03:19:23'),
(272, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.3.8', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Physical and environmental security >  Control', 'Procedures shall be established for monitoring and alarming when physical or environmental security is compromised.', '2022-02-25 03:19:43', '2022-02-25 03:19:43'),
(273, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.3.9', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Physical and environmental security >  Control', 'Procedures should be established and audited with respect to the addition, removal, and disposal of all assets.', '2022-02-25 03:20:00', '2022-02-25 03:20:00'),
(274, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.3.10', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Physical and environmental security >  Control', 'Procedures shall be established to ensure the protection of criticalcomponents during the interruption of operations, for example, due to fire, water ingress, security breach, interruption, or natural or any other type of disaster.', '2022-02-25 03:20:22', '2022-02-25 03:20:22'),
(275, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.4.1', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Network segmentation >  Control', 'A network segmentation countermeasure strategy employing security zones shall be developed for IACS devices based upon the risk level of the IACS.', '2022-02-25 03:20:39', '2022-02-25 03:20:39'),
(276, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.4.2', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Network segmentation >  Control', 'High-risk IACS shall be isolated from or employ a barrier device to separate it from other zones with different security levels or risks.', '2022-02-25 03:20:57', '2022-02-25 03:20:57'),
(277, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.4.3', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Network segmentation >  Control', 'Barrier devices shall block all non-essential communications in and out of the security zone containing critical control equipment.', '2022-02-25 03:21:12', '2022-02-25 03:21:12'),
(278, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.5.1', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Access control: Account administration >  Control', 'Access privileges implemented for access accounts shall be established in accordance with the organizations authorization security policy (see 4.3.3.7.1).', '2022-02-25 03:21:32', '2022-02-25 03:21:32'),
(279, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.5.2', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Access control: Account administration >  Control', 'As for all cyber security controls, the choice of access accounts for individuals versus access accounts for a crew shall be determined by considering threats, risks, and vulnerabilities. In this case, considerations include HSE risks of individual controls, mitigation using complementary physical security controls, requirement for accountability, and administrative/operational need.', '2022-02-25 03:21:54', '2022-02-25 03:21:54'),
(280, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.5.3', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Access control: Account administration >  Control', 'Access shall be granted, changed, or terminated on the authority of an appropriate manager.', '2022-02-25 03:22:10', '2022-02-25 03:22:10'),
(281, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.5.4', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Access control: Account administration >  Control', 'A record shall be maintained of all access accounts, including details of the individual(s) and devices authorized to use the account, their permissions, and the authorizing manager.', '2022-02-25 03:22:27', '2022-02-25 03:22:27');
INSERT INTO `clauses` (`id`, `standard_id`, `parent_id`, `number`, `title`, `description`, `created_at`, `updated_at`) VALUES
(282, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.5.5', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Access control: Account administration >  Control', 'Access accounts shall be suspended or removed as soon as they are no longer needed (for example, job change).', '2022-02-25 03:22:43', '2022-02-25 03:22:43'),
(283, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.5.6', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Access control: Account administration >  Control', 'All established access accounts shall be reviewed regularly to ensure that the individual(s) and devices have only the minimum required permissions.', '2022-02-25 03:22:59', '2022-02-25 03:22:59'),
(284, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.5.7', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Access control: Account administration >  Control', 'Default passwords for access accounts shall be changed before the IACS is put into service.', '2022-02-25 03:23:13', '2022-02-25 03:23:13'),
(285, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.5.8', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Access control: Account administration >  Control', 'Periodic reviews of compliance to the account administration policy should be performed.', '2022-02-25 03:23:28', '2022-02-25 03:23:28'),
(286, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.6.1', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Access control: Authentication >  Control', 'Companies shall have an authentication strategy or approach that defines the method(s) of authentication to be used.', '2022-02-25 03:23:44', '2022-02-25 03:23:44'),
(287, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.6.2', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Access control: Authentication >  Control', 'All users shall be authenticated before using the requested application, unless there are compensating combinations of entrance control technologies and administrative practices.', '2022-02-25 03:24:00', '2022-02-25 03:24:00'),
(288, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.6.3', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Access control: Authentication >  Control', 'Strong authentication practices (such as requiring strong passwords) shall be used on all system administrator and application configuration access accounts.', '2022-02-25 03:24:16', '2022-02-25 03:24:16'),
(289, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.6.4', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Access control: Authentication >  Control', 'Log files should record all access attempts to critical systems and should be reviewed for successful and failed access attempts.', '2022-02-25 03:24:33', '2022-02-25 03:24:33'),
(290, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.6.5', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Access control: Authentication >  Control', 'The organization shall employ an authentication scheme with an appropriate level of strength to positively identify a remote interactive user.', '2022-02-25 03:24:52', '2022-02-25 03:24:52'),
(291, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.6.6', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Access control: Authentication >  Control', 'The organization shall develop a policy addressing remote login by a user and/or remote connections (for example, task-to-task connections) to the control system which defines appropriate system responses to failed login attempts and periods of inactivity.', '2022-02-25 03:25:10', '2022-02-25 03:25:10'),
(292, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.6.7', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Access control: Authentication >  Control', 'After some number of failed login attempts by a remote user, the system should disable the access account for a certain amount of time.', '2022-02-25 03:25:26', '2022-02-25 03:25:26'),
(293, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.6.8', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Access control: Authentication >  Control', 'After a defined period of inactivity, a remote user should be required to re-authenticate before he or she can re-access the system.', '2022-02-25 03:25:49', '2022-02-25 03:25:49'),
(294, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.6.9', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Access control: Authentication >  Control', 'Systems should employ appropriate authentication schemes for task-to-task communication between applications and devices.', '2022-02-25 03:26:05', '2022-02-25 03:26:05'),
(295, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.7.1', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Access control: Authorization >  Control', 'Rules that define the privileges authorized under access accounts for personnel in various job roles shall be defined in an authorization security policy that is clearly documented and applied to all personnel upon authentication.', '2022-02-25 03:26:21', '2022-02-25 03:26:21'),
(296, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.7.2', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Access control: Authorization >  Control', 'The permission to access IACS devices shall be logical (rules that grant or deny access to known users based on their roles), physical (locks, cameras, and other controls that restrict access to an active computer console), or both.', '2022-02-25 03:26:38', '2022-02-25 03:26:38'),
(297, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.7.3', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Access control: Authorization >  Control', 'Access accounts should be role based to manage access to appropriate information or systems for that users role. Safety implications shall be considered when defining roles.', '2022-02-25 03:27:00', '2022-02-25 03:27:00'),
(298, 4, NULL, '4.3.3.7.4', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Selected security countermeasures > Access control: Authorization >  Control', 'In critical control environments, multiple authorization methods should be employed to limit access to the IACS.', '2022-02-25 03:27:16', '2022-02-25 03:27:16'),
(299, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.2.1', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > Risk management and implementation >  Control', 'The organization shall adopt a risk management framework that includes selection and implementation of IACS devices and countermeasures to manage risk to an acceptable level over the life of the facility.', '2022-02-25 03:27:34', '2022-02-25 03:27:34'),
(300, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.2.2', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > Risk management and implementation >  Control', 'A common defined set of countermeasures (technical and administrative) to address both physical and cyber security risks should be defined and applied across the organization wherever a specific risk is identified.', '2022-02-25 03:27:50', '2022-02-25 03:27:50'),
(301, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.3.1', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > System development and maintenance >  Control', 'The security functions and capabilities of each new component of the IACS shall be defined up front, developed or achieved via procurement, and tested together with other components so that the entire system meets the desired security profile.', '2022-02-25 03:28:11', '2022-02-25 03:28:11'),
(302, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.3.2', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > System development and maintenance >  Control', 'A change management system for the IACS environment shall be developed and implemented. The change management process shall follow separation of duty principles to avoid conflicts of interest', '2022-02-25 03:28:28', '2022-02-25 03:28:28'),
(303, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.3.3', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > System development and maintenance >  Control', 'Using clearly defined criteria, proposed changes to the IACS shall be reviewed for their potential impact to HSE risks and cyber security risks by individuals technically knowledgeable about the industrial operation and the IACS system.', '2022-02-25 03:28:46', '2022-02-25 03:28:46'),
(304, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.3.4', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > System development and maintenance >  Control', 'The security requirements of a new system being installed in the IACS environment in an existing zone shall meet the security policies and procedures required for that zone/environment. Similarly, maintenance upgrades or changes shall meet the security requirements for the zone.', '2022-02-25 03:29:02', '2022-02-25 03:29:02'),
(305, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.3.5', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > System development and maintenance >  Control', 'Cyber security change management procedures should be integrated with existing PSM procedures.', '2022-02-25 03:29:19', '2022-02-25 03:29:19'),
(306, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.3.6', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > System development and maintenance >  Control', 'The operations and change management policies and procedures shall be reviewed and kept current to ensure that security changes do not increase risks to safety or business continuity.', '2022-02-25 03:29:35', '2022-02-25 03:29:35'),
(307, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.3.7', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > System development and maintenance >  Control', 'A procedure for patch management shall be established, documented, and followed.', '2022-02-25 03:29:52', '2022-02-25 03:29:52'),
(308, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.3.8', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > System development and maintenance >  Control', 'A procedure for antivirus/malware management shall be established, documented, and followed', '2022-02-25 03:30:09', '2022-02-25 03:30:09'),
(309, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.3.9', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > System development and maintenance >  Control', 'A procedure for backing up and restoring computer systems and protecting backup copies shall be established, used, and verified by appropriate testing.', '2022-02-25 03:30:26', '2022-02-25 03:30:26'),
(310, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.4.1', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > Information and document management >  Control', 'A lifecycle document management process shall be developed and maintained for IACS information.', '2022-02-25 03:30:42', '2022-02-25 03:30:42'),
(311, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.4.2', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > Information and document management >  Control', 'Information classification levels (for example, company confidential, restricted, or public) shall be defined for access and control, including sharing, copying, transmitting, and distributing appropriate for the level of protection required.', '2022-02-25 03:30:58', '2022-02-25 03:30:58'),
(312, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.4.3', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > Information and document management >  Control', 'All logical assets within the scope of the CSMS (that is, control system design information, vulnerability assessments, network diagrams, and industrial operations programs) shall be classified to indicate the protection required commensurate with the consequences of unauthorized disclosure or modification.', '2022-02-25 03:31:15', '2022-02-25 03:31:15'),
(313, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.4.4', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > Information and document management >  Control', 'Policies and procedures should be developed detailing retention, physical and integrity protection, destruction, and disposal of all assets based on their classifications, including written and electronic records, equipment and other media containing information, with consideration for legal or regulatory requirements.', '2022-02-25 03:31:34', '2022-02-25 03:31:34'),
(314, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.4.5', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > Information and document management >  Control', 'Appropriate measures should be employed to ensure long-term records can be retrieved ( that is, converting the data to a newer format or retaining older equipment that can read the data).', '2022-02-25 03:31:53', '2022-02-25 03:31:53'),
(315, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.4.6', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > Information and document management >  Control', 'Information that requires special control or handling should be reviewed on a periodic basis to validate that special handling is still required.', '2022-02-25 03:32:09', '2022-02-25 03:32:09'),
(316, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.4.7', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > Information and document management >  Control', 'Periodic reviews of compliance to the information and document management policy should be performed', '2022-02-25 03:32:25', '2022-02-25 03:32:25'),
(317, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.5.1', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > Incident planning and response >  Control', 'The organization shall implement an incident response plan that identifies responsible personnel and defines actions to be performed by designated individuals.', '2022-02-25 03:32:41', '2022-02-25 03:32:41'),
(318, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.5.2', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > Incident planning and response >  Control', 'The incident response plan shall be communicated to all appropriate organizations.', '2022-02-25 03:32:57', '2022-02-25 03:32:57'),
(319, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.5.3', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > Incident planning and response >  Control', 'The organization should establish a reporting procedure to communicate unusual activities and events that may actually be cyber security incidents.', '2022-02-25 03:33:12', '2022-02-25 03:33:12'),
(320, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.5.4', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > Incident planning and response >  Control', 'Employees should be educated on their responsibility to report cyber security incidents and the methods of reporting these incidents.', '2022-02-25 03:33:28', '2022-02-25 03:33:28'),
(321, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.5.5', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > Incident planning and response >  Control', 'The organization should report cyber security incidents in a timely manner.', '2022-02-25 03:33:44', '2022-02-25 03:33:44'),
(322, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.5.6', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > Incident planning and response >  Control', 'If an incident is identified, the organization shall promptly respond in accordance with the established procedures.', '2022-02-25 03:34:01', '2022-02-25 03:34:01'),
(323, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.5.7', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > Incident planning and response >  Control', 'The organization should have procedures in place to identify failed and successful cyber security breaches.', '2022-02-25 03:34:17', '2022-02-25 03:34:17'),
(324, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.5.8', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > Incident planning and response >  Control', 'The details of an identified incident shall be documented to record the incident, the response, the lessons learned, and any actions taken to modify the CSMS in light of this incident.', '2022-02-25 03:34:32', '2022-02-25 03:34:32'),
(325, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.5.9', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > Incident planning and response >  Control', 'The documented details of an incident shall be communicated to all appropriate organizations ( that is, management, IT, process safety, automation and control engineering, security and manufacturing) in a timely manner.', '2022-02-25 03:34:47', '2022-02-25 03:34:47'),
(326, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.5.10', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > Incident planning and response >  Control', 'The organization shall have a business methodology in place to address issues discovered and ensure they are corrected.', '2022-02-25 03:35:03', '2022-02-25 03:35:03'),
(327, 4, NULL, '4.3.4.5.11', 'Addressing risk with the CSMS > Implementation > Incident planning and response >  Control', 'Drills should be conducted to test the incident response program on a routine basis.', '2022-02-25 03:35:27', '2022-02-25 03:35:27'),
(328, 4, NULL, '4.4.2.1', 'Monitoring and Improving the CSMS > Conformance >  Control', 'The audit program shall specify the methodology of the audit process.', '2022-02-25 03:35:43', '2022-02-25 03:35:43'),
(329, 4, NULL, '4.4.2.2', 'Monitoring and Improving the CSMS > Conformance >  Control', 'Validate that the IACS conforms to the CSMS. The CSMS shall include periodic audits of the IACS to validate that the security policies and procedures are performing as intended and meet the security objectives for the zone.', '2022-02-25 03:36:00', '2022-02-25 03:36:00'),
(330, 4, NULL, '4.4.2.3', 'Monitoring and Improving the CSMS > Conformance >  Control', 'The organization should define performance indicators and success criteria to monitor conformance to the CSMS. The results from each periodic audit should be expressed in the form of performance against these metrics to display security performance and security trends.', '2022-02-25 03:36:19', '2022-02-25 03:36:19'),
(331, 4, NULL, '4.4.2.4', 'Monitoring and Improving the CSMS > Conformance >  Control', 'A list of documents and reports required to establish an audit trail shall be developed.', '2022-02-25 03:36:35', '2022-02-25 03:36:35'),
(332, 4, NULL, '4.4.2.5', 'Monitoring and Improving the CSMS > Conformance >  Control', 'The organization shall state what non-conformance with the CSMS means, and any related punitive measures shall also be defined.', '2022-02-25 03:36:50', '2022-02-25 03:36:50'),
(333, 4, NULL, '4.4.2.6', 'Monitoring and Improving the CSMS > Conformance >  Control', 'The required competency for auditing the specific systems that are in scope should be specified. The level of independence required should be determined as part of the governance.', '2022-02-25 03:37:06', '2022-02-25 03:37:06'),
(334, 4, NULL, '4.4.3.1', 'Monitoring and Improving the CSMS > Review, improve, and maintain the CSMS >  Control', 'An organization shall be assigned to manage and coordinate the refinement and implementation of the CSMS changes and use a defined method in making and implementing changes.', '2022-02-25 03:37:22', '2022-02-25 03:37:22'),
(335, 4, NULL, '4.4.3.2', 'Monitoring and Improving the CSMS > Review, improve, and maintain the CSMS >  Control', 'The managing organization shall periodically evaluate the overall CSMS to ensure the security objectives are being met.', '2022-02-25 03:37:41', '2022-02-25 03:37:41'),
(336, 4, NULL, '4.4.3.3', 'Monitoring and Improving the CSMS > Review, improve, and maintain the CSMS >  Control', 'The organization should establish a list of triggers with set thresholds, which would result in a review of related elements of the CSMS and perhaps a change. These triggers include at a minimum: occurrence of serious security incidents, legal and regulatory changes, changes in risk, and major changes to the IACS. The thresholds should be based on the organizations risk tolerance.', '2022-02-25 03:37:56', '2022-02-25 03:37:56'),
(337, 4, NULL, '4.4.3.4', 'Monitoring and Improving the CSMS > Review, improve, and maintain the CSMS >  Control', 'The organization shall identify and implement appropriate corrective and preventive actions that modify the CSMS to meet security objectives.', '2022-02-25 03:38:12', '2022-02-25 03:38:12'),
(338, 4, NULL, '4.4.3.5', 'Monitoring and Improving the CSMS > Review, improve, and maintain the CSMS >  Control', 'A review of the organizations tolerance for risk should be initiated when there are major changes to the organization, technology, business objectives, internal business, and external events, including identified threats and changes in social climate.', '2022-02-25 03:38:28', '2022-02-25 03:38:28'),
(339, 4, NULL, '4.4.3.6', 'Monitoring and Improving the CSMS > Review, improve, and maintain the CSMS >  Control', 'Management system owners should monitor the industry for CSMS best practices for risk assessment and risk mitigation and evaluate their applicability.', '2022-02-25 03:38:46', '2022-02-25 03:38:46'),
(340, 4, NULL, '4.4.3.7', 'Monitoring and Improving the CSMS > Review, improve, and maintain the CSMS >  Control', 'The organization shall identify applicable and changing legislation relevant to cyber security.', '2022-02-25 03:39:02', '2022-02-25 03:39:02'),
(341, 4, NULL, '4.4.3.8', 'Monitoring and Improving the CSMS > Review, improve, and maintain the CSMS >  Control', 'Employee feedback on security suggestions should be actively sought and reported back to senior management as appropriate on performance shortcomings and opportunities.', '2022-02-25 03:39:23', '2022-02-25 03:39:23');
